*Telugu: [[పరాగ సంపర్కము]] (paraaga saMparkamu)

== SELF POLLINATION ==
Self Pollination is the transfer of pollen grains from the anther to the stigma of a plant, of the same species

===Translations===
*Telugu: [[ఆత్మ పరాగ సంపర్కము]] (aatma paraaga saMparkamu)

== CROSS POLLINATION ==
Cross Pollination is the transfer of pollen grains from the anther of a plant, to the stigma of another plant.

===Translations===
*Telugu: [[పర పరాగ సంపర్కము]] (para paraaga saMparkamu)
